{"tid":1607231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日係大戰,但唔係決戰","createTime":"2019-09-30T18:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T18:39:01.000Z","uid":301773,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d724fdb6334ffc9688a9f2bbe3a96cd587ea560c","tid":1607231,"uid":301773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T18:37:31.000Z","msg":"大家一定要記著<br />\n聽日 國殉日 既大戰 <br />\n唔係決戰<br />\n我地第一重點既係落鳩佢面<br />\n要佢做唔到歌舞昇平既假象<br />\n但要記著<br />\n聽日絕對唔係決戰<br />\n就算贏左都唔係完場<br />\n唔可以再用手足既犧牲去換一場半場既戰役<br />\n全力玩狗<br />\n然後極速撤退要佢一個都拉唔到<br />\n比同佢硬碰到底係更加令對方無面<br />\n請大家記實一句<br />\n聽日一齊出去既<br />\n一定要一齊返到去"},{"pid":"c5006a5875597f88d26b5c0c190c22af7125ca40","tid":1607231,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T18:38:29.000Z","msg":"Tui<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf60b8588f61d74ec194c18cda5834dd450aaa95","tid":1607231,"uid":170445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T18:39:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}